        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "Define the `determinant_3x3` function and calculate the determinants for x, y, and z by replacing the respective columns with the independent terms and using the defined function. Finally, print these determinants.\n",
        "\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
