        "## Resolver el sistema\n",
        "\n",
        "### Subtask:\n",
        "Dividir el determinante de cada variable por el determinante principal para encontrar el valor de cada variable.\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "markdown",
      "metadata": {
        "id": "fd10c071"
      },
      "source": [
        "**Reasoning**:\n",
        "Check if the main determinant is zero and calculate the values of x, y, and z if it is not.\n",
        "\n"
      ]
    },
    {
      "cell_type": "code",
      "metadata": {
        "colab": {
          "base_uri": "https://localhost:8080/"
        },
        "id": "2d34a358",
        "outputId": "b39836d7-532a-44cc-c679-947226b052bc"
      },
      "source": [
        "if det_main == 0:\n",
        "    print(\"The system has no unique solution and cannot be solved by Cramer's rule.\")\n",
        "else:\n",
        "    x = det_x / det_main\n",
        "    y = det_y / det_main\n",
        "    z = det_z / det_main\n",
        "    print(\"The solution is:\")\n",
        "    print(\"x =\", x)\n",
        "    print(\"y =\", y)\n",
        "    print(\"z =\", z)"
      ],
      "execution_count": 4,
